        <P>This page is specifically devoted to providing free trainings for addiction and mental health practitioners.
            All trainigs meet the requirements of the North Carolina Addiction Specialist Practice Board and have approval numbers
            for each training. Trainings are provided by qulified expert clinicans with significant
            clinical practice experience. These trainings represent the most current trends in the addiction profession
            and provide participates with journal articles to expand one's knowledge related to the topic.</P> 
            
        

