<div class="description">Advanced Clinical Supervision: Skills and Strategies
    Building on foundational supervision concepts, this advanced module addresses 
    methods for giving constructive feedback, evaluating performance, and navigating 
    supervisee resistance. The course also emphasizes cultural humility and strategies 
    to develop supervisees competencies in evidence-based practices. Counselors 
    completing this training will sharpen their abilities to mentor, coach, and 
    facilitate ongoing professional development within their clinical teams.
    <a href="about_us.html"><br>Click Here To Access Training Page</a>

    </div>
 
    

</div>
<div class="gallery">
